OL,3,CMum's plea to PM over 'Postcode
OL,4,Clottery' of care for dying children
OL,6,FIt comes as a leading children's
OL,7,Fpalliative care charity warned that
OL,8,Ffamilies of dying children face a
OL,9,F"postcode lottery" of care.
OL,11,FTogether for Short Lives said access
OL,12,Fto 24/7 end-of-life care at home is
OL,13,F"far too inconsistent" from region to
OL,14,Fregion.
OL,16,FA new report by the charity states
OL,17,Fthat as a result, families have to
OL,18,F"endure unnecessary hospital
OL,19,Fadmissions, delayed discharges and a
OL,20,Flack of choice and control".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@RO]uD@AOUuD@VO]zD@AOU|D@[O]
