OL,3,CMum's plea to PM over 'Postcode
OL,4,Clottery' of care for dying children
OL,6,FUnder a fifth of local health bodies
OL,7,Fspecifically "formally" plan and fund
OL,8,F24/7 at-home end-of-life care for
OL,9,Fchildren, the charity said.
OL,11,FIt said this means that families
OL,12,Fliving in some parts of the country
OL,13,Fwho are caring for a seriously ill
OL,14,Fchild stand a "much better chance"
OL,15,Fthan families in other areas to enable
OL,16,Ftheir child to die at home, if that is
OL,17,Fwhat they want.
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@WO]vD@OOUvD@bO]
