OL,3,CMum's plea to PM over 'Postcode
OL,4,Clottery' of care for dying children
OL,6,F"Ultimately it was because of that and
OL,7,Fthe goodwill of nurses who wanted to
OL,8,Fhelp despite the barriers they faced."
OL,10,FFriends and family took shifts to be
OL,11,Fwith Oliver through the night, and
OL,12,Fnurses worked extra hours to cover the
OL,13,Fcare he needed.
OL,15,FMs Buchanan added: "It was where we
OL,16,Fwanted him to die, surrounded by the
OL,17,Flove of his family, the green fields,
OL,18,Fthe sound of nature and just peace.
OL,19,FBut to get to that point cost a lot.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@fO]wD@TOU
