OL,3,CMum's plea to PM over 'Postcode
OL,4,Clottery' of care for dying children
OL,6,F"I honestly thought that when your
OL,7,Fchild is dying, you would have 24/7
OL,8,Fcare at home. But it turns out that
OL,9,Fjust isn't the case.
OL,11,F"Most of the time it was done by
OL,12,Fmyself and my family, and a patchwork
OL,13,Fof goodwill from various nursing care
OL,14,Fproviders. But we never knew if we'd
OL,15,Fhave cover from one week to the next,
OL,16,Fthere was no security.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
