OL,3,CMum's plea to PM over 'Postcode
OL,4,Clottery' of care for dying children
OL,6,F"In the end, Oliver died peacefully
OL,7,Fand without pain. It was a good
OL,8,Fexperience if you can describe it as
OL,9,Fthat and I am very aware of how this
OL,10,Ftime can unravel for families,
OL,11,Fespecially without the right support.
OL,12,FWe count ourselves lucky."
OL,14,FMs Buchanan has written an open letter
OL,15,Fto Sir Keir urging him to review how
OL,16,Fpalliative care for children is funded.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
