OL,3,CMum's plea to PM over 'Postcode
OL,4,Clottery' of care for dying children
OL,6,F"Families like mine aren't getting the
OL,7,Fcare they need and aren't able to make
OL,8,Fchoices about their child's end of
OL,9,Flife, because of where they live," she
OL,10,Fwrote.
OL,12,F"So many feel abandoned and
OL,13,Foverwhelmed by a system that is
OL,14,Ffailing them."
OL,16,FTogether for Short Lives says funding
OL,17,Fshortfalls, workforce shortages and a
OL,18,Flack of leadership and accountability
OL,19,Fare contributing to the postcode
OL,20,Flottery of care across the UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@bO]tD@AOUvD@NO]
