OL,3,CMum's plea to PM over 'Postcode
OL,4,Clottery' of care for dying children
OL,6,FIt has estimated that the funding gap
OL,7,Fis one of the main barriers which has
OL,8,Fcreated these inconsistencies in
OL,9,Fchildren's end-of-life care.
OL,11,FIn England alone, the charity
OL,12,Festimates there is a #310-million
OL,13,Ffunding gap for the NHS to deliver
OL,14,Fchildren's end-of-life care.
OL,16,FMany families have told the charity
OL,17,Fthat they felt abandoned and
OL,18,Foverwhelmed after their child was
OL,19,Fdiagnosed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
