OL,3,CMum's plea to PM over 'Postcode
OL,4,Clottery' of care for dying children
OL,6,FNick Carroll, chief executive of
OL,7,FTogether for Short Lives, said: "For
OL,8,Ftoo long, seriously ill children and
OL,9,Ftheir families across England have
OL,10,Fbeen failed by a system which has been
OL,11,Fpersistently underfunded and under
OL,12,Fprioritised. It says a lot that Clare
OL,13,Fhad to fight to have the end-of-life
OL,14,Fexperience she wanted for her son
OL,15,FOliver.
OL,17,F"The UK Government must act urgently
OL,18,Fby holding a full review into the way
OL,19,Fchildren's palliative care is planned
OL,20,Fand funded in England.
OL,26,@oD@aOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
