OL,3,CMum's plea to PM over 'Postcode
OL,4,Clottery' of care for dying children
OL,6,F"We know that public finances are
OL,7,Funder pressure, yet the money needed
OL,8,Fto fix the issues across children's
OL,9,Fpalliative care is tiny when compared
OL,10,Fto the annual NHS England budget.
OL,12,F"What we need is the will of those in
OL,13,Fpower to act ` so that mums like Clare
OL,14,Fcan spend less time fighting to get
OL,15,Fthe care their child needs and more
OL,16,Ftime making the most of the short time
OL,17,Fthey have together.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
