OL,3,CMum's plea to PM over 'Postcode
OL,4,Clottery' of care for dying children
OL,6,F"If ministers are to achieve their
OL,7,Faims of shifting care from hospitals
OL,8,Finto the community in the next decade,
OL,9,Fwe urgently need a children's
OL,10,Fpalliative care system that's built to
OL,11,Flast."
OL,13,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,14,Fspokesperson said: "Our sympathies are
OL,15,Fwith all families requiring end-of-
OL,16,Flife care for a child.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@FO]vD@TOU
