OL,6,F"We recently announced the biggest
OL,7,Finvestment in hospices in a
OL,8,Fgeneration: #100 million to improve
OL,9,Ffacilities and allow them to focus
OL,10,Fwider resources on patient care.
OL,11,FHospices for children and young people
OL,12,Fwill also receive a further #26
OL,13,Fmillion.
OL,15,F"We are working to make sure the
OL,16,Fsector is sustainable in the long
OL,17,Fterm, and this government is
OL,18,Fdetermined to shift more healthcare
OL,19,Fout of hospitals and into the
OL,20,Fcommunity through our Plan for Change."
